21 race meeting;
22 b. In the Kentucky standardbred development fund established in
23 KRS 230.770, if the host track is conducting a harness race
24 meeting or the interstate wagering is conducted on a harness race
25 meeting;
26 c. In the Kentucky paint horse, Appaloosa, and Arabian development
27 fund established by KRS 230.445, if the host track is conducting a
